Class FoodEntry

object.Entry
object.FoodEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class FoodEntry extends Entry
Represents a food-related entry in the system.

This class extends Entry. A FoodEntry specifies the food item, the number of portions, and the weight in grams per portion. It calculates calories based on these values and the food's calories per gram.
